Package com.seailz.discordjv.model.message

Record Class Attachment

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.seailz.discordjv.model.message.Attachment
Record Components:
id - The attachment ID.
fileName - The name of the file attached.
description - The attachment description.
type - The attachment MIME type.
size - The size of the file in bytes.
url - The source URL of the file.
proxyUrl - A proxied URL of the file.
height - The height of the file (if image).
width - The width of the file (if image).
ephemeral - Whether this attachment is ephemeral.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Compilerable, Resolvable
public record Attachment(String id, String fileName, String description, String type, int size, String url, String proxyUrl, int height, int width, boolean ephemeral) extends Record implements Compilerable, Resolvable
Represents a message attachment.
